 9:56
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='585000' id='t-585000'>So organizing these markets is one thing we try to do.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='588000' id='t-588000'>Now we have taken on a second thing, and this gets to my wish.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='592000' id='t-592000'>It has been my experience in working in developing countries</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='597000' id='t-597000'>that while the headlines may all be -- the pessimistic headlines may say,</span>
