11:34
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='683000' id='t-683000'>And the test is: one, will it do the job?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='685000' id='t-685000'>Will it provide high quality care?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='688000' id='t-688000'>And two, will it do it at a price</span>
