12:38
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='747000' id='t-747000'>The person, in my view,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='750000' id='t-750000'>who has done the best job of this in the health care area,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='755000' id='t-755000'>of building a system in a very poor area, is Dr. Paul Farmer,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='759000' id='t-759000'>who, many of you know, has worked for now 20 years with his group,</span>
