<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='795000' id='t-795000'>So when we decided to work in Rwanda</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='799000' id='t-799000'>on trying to dramatically increase the income of the country and fight the AIDS problem,</span>
