<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='814000' id='t-814000'>So I rang up, asked Paul Farmer if he would help.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='819000' id='t-819000'>Because it seemed to me if we could prove there was a model in Haiti</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='822000' id='t-822000'>and a model in Rwanda that we could then take all over the country,</span>
