<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='840000' id='t-840000'>And so we have set about doing that.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:15
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='844000' id='t-844000'>Now, we started working together 18 months ago.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='848000' id='t-848000'>And we're working in an area called Southern Kayonza,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='852000' id='t-852000'>which is one of the poorest areas in Rwanda,</span>
