<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='929000' id='t-929000'>I'll tell you a little bit about our team because it's indicative of what we do.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='933000' id='t-933000'>We have about 500 people around the world</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='936000' id='t-936000'>working in our AIDS program, some of them for nothing --</span>
