<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='942000' id='t-942000'>And then we have others working in these other related programs.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='946000' id='t-946000'>Our business plan in Rwanda</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='948000' id='t-948000'>was put together under the leadership of Diana Noble,</span>
