<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1031000' id='t-1031000'>again, all preventable and treatable.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1034000' id='t-1034000'>And not a single soul in this area was being treated for AIDS or tuberculosis.</span>
</span>
