<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1040000' id='t-1040000'>Within the first 18 months, the following things happened:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1044000' id='t-1044000'>we went from zero to about 2,000 people being treated for AIDS.</span>
