<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
18:36
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1105000' id='t-1105000'>We've started the first malaria treatment programs they've ever had there.</span>
